<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.elsevier.com/wps/find/S04.cws_home/books" class="external text" title="http://www.elsevier.com/wps/find/S04.cws_home/books" rel="nofollow">Economics and Finance - Elsevier</a></li>
