<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> Kobasa, Paul A. "Encyclopedia." World Book Online Reference Center. 2008. [Place of access.] 13 Jan. 2008 &lt;<a href="http://www.worldbookonline.com/wb/Login?ed=wb&amp;tu=%2Fwb%2FArticle%3Fid%3Dar180800" class="external free" title="http://www.worldbookonline.com/wb/Login?ed=wb&amp;tu=%2Fwb%2FArticle%3Fid%3Dar180800" rel="nofollow">http://www.worldbookonline.com/wb/Login?ed=wb&amp;tu=%2Fwb%2FArticle%3Fid%3Dar180800</a>&gt;</li>
<li id="cite_note-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://linuxreviews.org/news/2004/07/07_3000k/" class="external text" title="http://linuxreviews.org/news/2004/07/07_3000k/" rel="nofollow">"Wikipedia Passes 300,000 Articles making it the worlds largest encyclopedia"</a>, <i>Linux Reviews</i>, 2004 July 7.</li>
</ol>
</div>
